headline: Leidos Helps Utilities and Developers Tackle AI Data Centers' Power Demands
summary: As these hyperscale data centers, designed to support AI and large-scale computing, drive unprecedented energy loads, Leidos works to help modernize the grid and enhance reliable power delivery NORTHAMPTON, MA / ACCESS Newswire / January 28, 2026 ...
